      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a vehicle of unrivaled caliber, maintained to exacting standards that define the 'mint' designation. This specimen exhibits flawless aesthetic integrity and mechanical precision, offering a driving experience indistinguishable from its original showroom debut. Every detail, from the pristine interior surfaces to the meticulously preserved powertrain, reflects a history of uncompromising care. For the discerning collector or enthusiast who accepts nothing less than perfection, this offering represents a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle in superlative condition.",
